            <h3>#@taskInfo.Id Task ( @taskInfo.TaskName )</h3>
            <p> <i class="far fa-edit"></i> Last updated by: <span>@user.FullName </span>@taskInfo.UpdateDate.Value.ToShortDateString() </p>
